Facebook was founded by Mark Zuckerberg along with fellow Harvard students Eduardo Saverin, Andrew McCollum, Dustin Moskovitz, and Chris Hughes.

Instagram was created by Kevin Systrom and Mike Krieger.

Snapchat was co-founded by Evan Spiegel and Bobby Murphy.

Twitter was launched by Jack Dorsey, Evan Williams, Biz Stone, and Noah Glass.

ByteDance, a Chinese company, created TikTok.
